snippet.title: Escape Academy: The Complete Edition - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Escape Academy: The Complete Edition is coming to Nintendo Switch fall 2023! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/escape-academy-the-complete-edition-switch/

Train to become the ultimate Escape Room master. Solve Puzzles. Hack Servers. Meet the Faculty. Brew the perfect cup of tea. Entirely playable in single player or co-op with a friend - local or online!

#EscapeAcademy #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com/
